<div id="content" data-mode="update" data-add="self" class="w-100 h-100 d-flex flex-column">
    <div class="section-header d-flex flex-nowrap align-items-center mb-4">
        <img src="/static/img/logo.svg" class="mh-100 me-3"/>
        <h1 class="mb-0 fs-2 flex-1">Setup</h1>
        <button id="roomOptionsOpenHelpBtn" class="btn btn-bkr-secondary icon-btn icon-help-circled align-self-end" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#roomOptionsHelp"></button>
    </div>
    <div class="section-img text-center"><img src="/static/img/room_settings.svg" alt="Room settings page" class="mh-100"/></div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-column my-4 card p-3">
        <label class="form-label mb-4 fw-bold text-center">Select a room type</label>
        <ul class="nav nav-pills justify-content-center gap-4" id="roomType" role="tablist">
            <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                <button class="nav-link icon-user d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center"
                        id="pills-individual-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-individual" data-val="individual"
                        type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-individual" aria-selected="false">Individual</button>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                <button class="nav-link icon-users d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center"
                        id="pills-group-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-group" data-val="group"
                        type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-group" aria-selected="false">Group</button>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tab-content flex-1 pb-4 text-center" id="pills-tabContent">
        <div class="form-check card flex-row p-3 ps-5">
            <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" name="assignUsernames" id="assignUsernames" checked="" />
            <label for="assignUsernames" class="form-check-label ms-2">Auto-Assign Usernames</label>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane mb-4 fade" id="pills-individual" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-individual-btn" tabindex="0">
            <div id="individualSubOptions" class="mt-4">
                <h6 class="mb-4">Individual Game Type:</h6>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4">
                    <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="individualType" id="individualSpeedBased"
                           checked="" autocomplete="off" value="individualSpeedBased">
                    <label class="btn btn-bkr-secondary icon-stopwatch" for="individualSpeedBased">Speed</label>
                    <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="individualType" id="individualScoreBased"
                           autocomplete="off" value="individualScoreBased">
                    <label class="btn btn-bkr-secondary icon-target" for="individualScoreBased">Score</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="pills-group" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="pills-group-btn" tabindex="0">
            <div id="groupSubOptions" class="d-flex flex-column gap-4 mt-4">
                <div class="form-check card flex-row p-3 ps-5">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" name="assignGroups" id="assignGroups" checked="" />
                    <label for="assignGroups" class="form-check-label ms-2">Auto-Assign Groups</label>
                </div>
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h6 class="my-0">Group Setup:</h6>
                    <ul class="nav nav-pills justify-content-center gap-4 my-4" id="" role="tablist">
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                            <button class="nav-link active" id="pills-auto-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-auto" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-auto" aria-selected="true">Auto</button>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                            <button class="nav-link" id="pills-custom-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-custom" type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-custom" aria-selected="false">Custom</button>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tab-content" id="pills-groupSetup">

                        <div id="pills-auto" class="tab-pane fade active show">
                            <div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
                                <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-numStudents"># of students</span>
                                <input type="number" class="form-control" name="numStudents" min="4" id="numStudents" aria-label="Number of students" aria-describedby="addon-numStudents">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="pills-custom" class="tab-pane fade">
                            <div class="input-group flex-nowrap mb-4">
                                <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-numGroups"># of groups</span>
                                <input type="number" class="form-control" name="numGroups" min="2" id="numGroups" aria-label="Number of groups" aria-describedby="addon-numGroups">
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
                                <span class="input-group-text" id="addon-groupSize">Group size</span>
                                <input type="number" class="form-control" name="numPerGroup" min="2" id="numPerGroup" aria-label="Number of students per group" aria-describedby="addon-groupSize">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h6 class="my-0">Group Game Mode:</h6>

                    <ul class="nav nav-pills justify-content-center gap-4 mt-4" id="groupType" role="tablist">
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                            <button class="nav-link active" id="pills-ofa-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-ofa"
                                    type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-ofa" aria-selected="true" data-val="oneForAll">One-for-All</button>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
                            <button class="nav-link" id="pills-ffa-btn" data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#pills-ffa"
                                    type="button" role="tab" aria-controls="pills-ffa" aria-selected="false" data-val="freeForAll">Free-for-All</button>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tab-content" id="pills-groupGameType">

                        <div id="pills-ofa" class="tab-pane fade active show">
                            <h6 class="my-4">One-For-All Game Type:</h6>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4">
                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="ofaType" id="OFASpeedBasedBtn"
                                       checked="" autocomplete="off" value="OFASpeedBased">
                                <label class="btn btn-bkr-secondary icon-stopwatch" for="OFASpeedBasedBtn">Speed</label>
                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="ofaType" id="OFAScoreBasedBtn"
                                       autocomplete="off" value="OFAScoreBased">
                                <label class="btn btn-bkr-secondary icon-target" for="OFAScoreBasedBtn">Score</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div id="pills-ffa" class="tab-pane fade">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-danger text-center mb-0 error-lbl mt-4">{{errorTxt}}</div>
        <input type="submit" class="form-control btn btn-bkr-confirm mt-4" id="submitRoomOptions" value="OK">
    </div>
</div>

<div id="roomOptionsHelp" class="modal fade" data-target="body" data-add="self" data-mode="append" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="roomOptionsHelpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header hstack gap-2">
                <h1 class="modal-title fs-2 flex-1" id="roomOptionsHelpModalLabel">Help</h1>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <h3>Game Modes:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Individual Mode:</b> In this mode, all of the players battle against each other. The first person
                        to answer correctly will be awarded points.</li>
                    <li><b>Group Mode:</b> In group mode, players can either work together and battle against other groups, or they
                        can battle the people within their own group.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Auto-Assign Options:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Auto-Assign Usernames:</b> A school-friendly username will automatically be assigned to the student. Disable this
                        option if you want to allow the students to type in their own usernames.</li>
                    <li><b>Auto-Assign Groups:</b> Students will be automatically assigned to groups based on the order that they join the game.
                        Disable this option to allow students to manually select their group number.</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Group Options:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><h5>Group Setup:</h5>
                        <span>You can let the computer automatically create/manage groups, or you can manually manage your groups.</span>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>Auto</b> - The computer will make an appropriate number of groups based on the number of students
                                you have in your class. A class of 41 students will typically create 8 groups.</li>
                            <li><b>Custom</b> - You can choose the number of groups and the number of students per group.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><h5>Group Game Mode:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>One-For-All</b> - Students work together in groups to battle other groups. However, only the <b><em>first</em></b> answer
                                from each group will be accepted.
                                <ul>
                                    <li><b>Speed Based Mode:</b> The first group to answer correctly wins that round and is awarded points.</li>
                                    <li><b>Score Based Mode:</b> All groups are able to respond and are awarded points based on quickly they answered compared
                                        to other groups.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li><b>Free-For-All</b> - Students will battle the other students in their group. In this mode, each student must submit an
                                answer before the game will progress.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


